1.0.name: wordpress/photo-sidebar-widget
1.0.description: The SmugMug Photo Sidebar widget displays a user-selectable number of random photos from one (or several) RSS photo feeds in the sidebar of a Word Press blog. New features in version 2.0 include multiple widget support and image caching (which may speed up page loads).
